1
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:14,760
Come in.

2
00:01:18,880 --> 00:01:20,520
The DNA test results are out.

3
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:21,880
The victim had no criminal record.

4
00:01:21,880 --> 00:01:24,120
So we can't identify him yet.

5
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:25,560
Understood.

6
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:29,520
Limbs broken and crushed like this.

7
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:31,800
The victim's limbs were...

8
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:32,880
...broken while he was alive.

9
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:55,760
Who is it? Stop knocking.

10
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,160
Who are you looking for?

11
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:05,720
I just...

12
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,680
...need to talk to you.

13
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:43,280
These masks are quite interesting.

14
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:48,840
It looks like several masks...

15
