24
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,280
Yes.

25
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,960
But this medicinal wine doesn't sell well.

26
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:18,120
So our shop launched this new product.

27
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:22,960
Usually men buy it for women.

28
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:26,640
L-L-L-Love Potion.

29
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,840
People come to the bar to spend money...

30
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,240
...isn't it just to buy happiness?

31
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,200
It's consensual.

32
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:33,200
What's the...

33
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,160
...b-big deal?

34
00:03:38,640 --> 00:03:40,960
Who handles the empty bottles and cardboard...

35
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:41,840
