119
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:01,880
There was a disturbance at the bar that day.

120
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:02,440
Yes.

121
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:04,880
It was chaos caused by a rich kid.

122
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:06,640
But none of the participants are missing,

123
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,120
and they've all been ruled out as suspects.

124
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:32,920
The incomplete pattern at the crime scene,

125
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,360
what exactly is it?

126
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:43,520
This back alley is so narrow,

127
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:45,440
