128
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:46,520
So what if it's narrow?

129
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:49,200
Just crush the person first,

130
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,880
then put them in a cardboard box.

131
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:51,760
And you're done.

132
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:54,040
That's not the point.

133
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,800
The purpose of dumping the body...

134
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:57,560
either it was close by

135
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,480
for convenience,

136
00:07:58,760 --> 00:07:59,960
or it was to

137
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:01,760
hide their own information

138
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:03,320
or the crime scene.

139
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:06,960
Meaning the crime scene

140
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:08,040
is right near the bar.

141
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,200
Perhaps there is another possibility,

142
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,080
that it's related to Occult arts.

143
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:18,200
Ai Xia died in her office.

144
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:20,120
Cheng Hui died in the casino he just took over.

145
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:22,400
This almost suggests that

146
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:24,120
