147
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:25,880
You mean

148
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:27,280
the victim and Zhiyin Bar

149
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:28,320
also have some connection?

150
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:32,120
Investigate Zhiyin Bar

151
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:34,000
and all suspicious locations around it.

152
00:08:34,560 --> 00:08:35,160
Also,

153
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:38,240
identify the victim as soon as possible.

154
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,320
Yes, sir.

155
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:47,800
Based on the autopsy report,

156
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,280
since the killer

157
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:51,000
tortured the victim for at least three days,

158
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:53,200
we can start with missing persons

159
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,560
to check the victim's identity.

160
00:09:06,880 --> 00:09:08,120
Sis,

161
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:11,880
