166
00:10:43,880 --> 00:10:45,600
Missing persons matching the deceased's profile...

167
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,400
There are over a dozen.

168
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:49,200
May I ask,

169
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:50,640
