170
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,400
If the killer

171
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:56,120
really chooses targets from the wish cards,

172
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,400
these wish cards

173
00:10:57,680 --> 00:10:59,520
can at least help us narrow down the scope.

174
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:02,600
Jiang Li.

175
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:03,920
Jiang Li!

176
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:07,360
Come look at this.

177
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:16,960
Didn't the Divine Tree only recently go viral?

178
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,280
How could Shen Qing have drawn this?

179
00:11:19,760 --> 00:11:21,000
Could it be that Shen Qing

180
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,240
found out the killer's secret,

181
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,040
and that's why...

182
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:26,760
We are getting closer to the truth.

183
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:28,400
Everything will come to light.

184
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:34,400
Since everything revolves around the Divine Tree,

185
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:36,640
Shen Man,

186
00:11:37,160 --> 00:11:38,920
use your resources to investigate

187
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:39,880
exactly who

188
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:42,120
created this Divine Tree wishing sanctuary.

189
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,040
Right.

190
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:44,480
Why didn't I think of that?

191
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,240
I'm heading out.

192
00:12:01,040 --> 00:12:02,000
Take a look at this.

193
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:06,240
This actually matches the deceased's condition.

194
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:08,520
But it's only signed with a letter.

195
00:12:14,880 --> 00:12:15,960
These three missing persons

196
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:17,480
have an "L" in their family members' names.

197
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:18,880
At least it narrows the range.

198
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:24,360
This family lives on Ancient Temple Street.

199
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:28,000
Isn't that near Zhiyin Bar?

200
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:44,640
Found it, Shen Man.

201
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:48,480
This is the entire internet's

202
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:50,040
very first video about the Divine Tree.

203
00:12:55,640 --> 00:12:57,720
Three days after this video was posted,

204
00:12:58,880 --> 00:12:59,920
Ai Xia died.

205
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:03,120
Can you find out who posted this video?

206
