I can't.

207
00:13:05,160 --> 00:13:06,520
They used a virtual address.

208
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:18,600
Hey, Da Jin.

209
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:27,480
Hello.

210
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,600
We'd like to ask about

211
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,760
