212
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:34,760
Please, come in.

213
00:13:48,560 --> 00:13:49,520
This is...

214
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:54,320
Ever since my husband went missing,

215
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:55,760
I joined the Mutual Aid Association.

216
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:57,400
We can stay in touch with each other.

217
00:14:00,160 --> 00:14:02,000
Please verify the information here.

218
00:14:02,280 --> 00:14:03,920
See if it matches your husband.

219
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:08,400
This is correct.

220
00:14:09,280 --> 00:14:10,600
This is also correct.

221
00:14:11,040 --> 00:14:12,040
These are all correct.

222
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:15,520
But...

223
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,760
my husband had surgery.

224
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:19,640
Near his brow bone,

225
00:14:19,640 --> 00:14:21,520
