228
00:14:37,240 --> 00:14:38,400
Don't give up hope.

229
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:41,920
Sorry to disturb you today.

230
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:43,560
Sorry for the intrusion.

231
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:04,880
The video was posted by this person.

232
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:07,240
Red Teardrop.

233
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:10,880
Move over.

234
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:20,200
What kind of crappy website is this?

235
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:22,240
