240
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:33,440
used the Divine Tree wishing method instead.

241
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:37,040
Can you find out where this Red Teardrop

242
00:15:37,040 --> 00:15:37,920
is right now?

243
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:40,400
I am Da Jin, after all.

244
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:44,600
Got a problem? Find Da Jin.

245
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:45,880
Get up.

246
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:57,240
The informant living on Ancient Temple Street

247
00:15:57,520 --> 00:15:59,120
turned out not to be the deceased's family.

248
00:16:01,120 --> 00:16:01,880
We'll have to check

249
00:16:01,880 --> 00:16:03,240
the other two missing persons' families.

250
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:15,880
Get up. Come on.

251
00:16:16,880 --> 00:16:17,520
Where are you going for fun?

252
00:16:17,520 --> 00:16:18,120
What's going on?

253
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:18,600
You drank so much.

254
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:19,520
Let big brother take you to sober you up.

255
00:16:19,520 --> 00:16:20,160
Wait a minute.

256
00:16:21,920 --> 00:16:22,720
Don't meddle.

257
00:16:23,640 --> 00:16:24,720
How did she get this drunk?

258
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:28,480
Do you know her?

259
00:16:29,480 --> 00:16:30,720
What is wrong with you?

260
00:16:31,040 --> 00:16:32,120
None of your business.

261
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:33,760
This guy's a psycho.

262
00:16:39,680 --> 00:16:41,000
I just got cursed at.

263
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:42,080
I heard.

264
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:44,280
The staff said so.

265
00:16:44,280 --> 00:16:45,600
Spending money to buy happiness.

266
00:16:52,760 --> 00:16:53,280
Hello?

267
00:16:53,760 --> 00:16:54,360
Jiang Li.

268
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:56,800
I found the person hyping up the Divine Tree.
